'''Amagraman''' ('''Dittrichia viscosa''') d imɣi iḥemlen imeṭqan i yetuneddan. Imusnawen n yimɣan, qqaren-ed, belli seg Lazi i yed-itac, akken ad yaɣ iri n yilel agrakal akked  Lurup neɣ amadal s umata. Imɣi n umagraman ittak anzi ɣer ''buzduz'' akked ''taysa'': Ad iṣbeḥ seg yiwet n txerrubt i yed-cetlen. Iferrawen n umagraman d izegzawen. Tizegzewt nsen ḥemqet. Mayella d talɣa nsen truḥ s teɣzef. Teɣzef i yettuferyen afray n tuɣmest.<span id="sous_titre_h1"></span><span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="111"></span>
== Tasnaẓɣurt [Aẓar n wawal] ==
'''Amagraman''' d awal uddis [''taguri tamawalt tuddist''] i yed-ikkan seg sin n wawalen: “ < <nowiki>''</nowiki>''amager<nowiki>''</nowiki> + <nowiki>''</nowiki>aman''<nowiki>''</nowiki>: Imɣi itmagaren aman. Taseklut [''Ccejra''] n umagraman qqaren-as medden <nowiki>'''</nowiki>Tamagramant<nowiki>'''</nowiki>.'' <br>Awal ayi n ''umagraman'' d amay amgut. Amedya: amṭiq ayi yeṭṭuqet s umagraman. Amgraman ur ad itett ara uɣelmi.

== Aglam ==
[[Tugna:Inflorescences Dittrichia viscosa.JPG|right|thumb|Ağğuğğey n umagraman]]
Amagraman d imɣi i ḥemlen imeṭqan i yetuneddan (< nda) = [''ideg llan waman'']; ɣas akken tikwal ittemɣay-ed deg iyufa (< ''ayafa''). Amagraman iğğuğğuy deg anebdu. Iğğeğğiyen ines werriɣet. Imɣi n umagraman izmer ad yaweṭ alammi d wazal n lmitra d wezgen deg teɣzef; mayella deg tehri, adarnuc-is, izmer ad yaweṭ alammi d lmitra. Ifrawen n umagraman tminṭaṭen am llazuq.

Imɣan-is tacen: imeqq-id ɣef yiri n yilel agrakal akken i yed-imeqqi deg Lurup akken mayella tella. 

