== Igan ==
'''Amagraman''' d imɣi amdawi: Ifer n umagraman iskussum tiggest (lğerḥ). Zik, m’ara yigges yemdan, deg lexla - anida ur yelli la qej la waj - ama d argaz neɣ d tameṭṭut, d aqcic neɣ d taqcict, ad iḥuf tamagramant, ad ilwu iferrawen-is, imir ad ten-ig ɣef tiggest i t-yuɣen, ad t-en-iṭṭef tiremt - akken meqqer tiggest: azal n 5 alammi d 10 n dqayq -, imir ad tekkusem tiggest 

Assexzen, ssexzanent medden d taɣ ebbart, neɣ d asɣar (n iferrawen).<span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="201"></span>

Aẓar n umagraman iddukul d dwa n [[iḥetwacen]]. Tdawin medden yes tusut, turin, tgr.

